Our study is based on a dataset of seven European pollinator networks compiled from the web-of-life dataset (see Materials and Methods), for which phylogenetic relationships (figs. S1 and S2) and information about plantsâ€™ functional traits (database S1) were gathered from various sources. Specifically, the seven networks belong to Mediterranean (
 
